Normal Skew Model fit Function

Source: R/HeckmanSK.R
HeckmanSK.Rd

Estimates the parameters of the Normal Skew model

HeckmanSK(
  selection,
  outcome,
  data = sys.frame(sys.parent()),
  lambda,
  start = NULL
)

Arguments

selection

Selection equation.
outcome

Primary Regression Equation.
data

Database.
lambda

Initial start for asymmetry parameter.
start

initial values.

Examples

data(MEPS2001)
attach(MEPS2001)

selectEq <- dambexp ~ age + female + educ + blhisp + totchr + ins + income

HeckmanSK(selectEq, outcomeEq, data = MEPS2001, lambda = 1)
